Price Reduction - $925,000!
A First Class Residence in a Premiere Location
It’s everything you’ve been looking for, spotlessly presented and stylishly renovated, this Executive home has been designed for a lifetime of enjoyment for the whole family. Set behind a secure front fence, nestled amongst manicured gardens front and rear on a flat 694m2 approx block, this is living on a grand scale.
Features 5 large bedrooms plus study (or 6th bedroom), master has WIR and quality new full ensuite. A wide driveway provides plenty of off street parking, the double garage has rear access with space to park a boat, extra cars or trailer. Extras include slab heating, ducted air conditioning plus split system air conditioning, and watertanks. Located in a prestigious part of Dandenong Central, amongst other quality homes, opposite St Johns College, with bus, Dandenong Plaza and your choice of Primary schools only moments away, it’s just perfect for the growing family. Come live the good life! Inspect today.

Description:
UNDER OFFER
Located in the heart of Dandenong within walking distance to Dandenong Plaza, Market and Train Station is this nicely presented, two bedroom gem with secure garage parking. Whether you are a first home buyer entering the market or an investor looking for a near positive addition to your growing portfolio, this one ticks all the boxes.
Upon entry you are greeted with a spacious formal living and dining area, perfect for entertaining with friends and family. The adjoining kitchen contains European appliances and ample bench, shelving and cupboard space, which are all conveniently placed to reduce clutter and help keep your kitchen stay neat and tidy.
The property boasts two sizeable bedrooms, one leading out onto the balcony. Both bedrooms have built in robes and are within close proximity to the separate toilet and bathroom/ laundry area. This property has had new carpets laid, has been freshly painted, and is ready for you to move straight in.
If you are looking for a secure investment or exceptional first home, this fantastic opportunity is not to be missed!
Thinking of selling? Call us today; Boronia office on 9761 2277, Wantirna office on 9800 1225, Rowville office on 9755 6666 or Bayswater office on 9720 3030.
TO REGISTER YOUR INTEREST click on either of the following tabs and fill in your details, BOOK AN INSPECTION on the Biggin & Scott website or EMAIL AGENT / CONTACTAGENT on Real Estate.com.au and other websites. You will be contacted by one of our agents and will also receive a text advising of inspection times.

Description:
Family-sized living, low maintenance ease
Providing family-sized accommodation in highly-desirable low maintenance surrounds, this impeccable 3-bedroom townhouse is brilliantly positioned for a carefree lifestyle where all essential amenities are conveniently within arms reach.
On a quiet street, just moments to the attractions of Dandenong Plaza, transport, schools and parks, this light-filled home boasts high ceilings throughout and features both a formal lounge and generous open plan living area where a well-equipped contemporary kitchen looks out across the casual family/dining area to the easy-care alfresco terrace.
All three bedrooms can be found upstairs, including the tranquil master with sparkling ensuite and walk-in robe; a full family bathroom services the remaining two bedrooms which both boast built-in wardrobes.
This stylish abode is sure to pique the interest of first home buyers, investors and young families thanks to its peaceful position in an amenity-rich locale, whilst electric heating, split system heating/cooling, solar panels and auto garage are all included and simply add to the homes already immense appeal.
